Jung Hyunwoo is just an unlucky gamer barely making ends meet in the VR game "God Wars." He even ends up losing access to his game account due to a horrible accident and is forced to create a new character. Now equipped with a mind-blowing skill and a legendary class, all that's left is for him to level up and go from zero to hero...
